item.title: 【Live Audios (lossy)】M4A - Sticky & Sweet Tour Cardiff Dress Rehearsal with Pre-Recorded Vocals (08.20.2008) WAV/M4A
item.description:
From a rehearsal for her 2008 - 2009 hit world tour: "Sticky & Sweet Tour" on August 20th, 2008 in Cardiff, Wales at Millennium Stadium.

Audio taken from a 1 hour and 45 minutes rehearsal soundboard audio with pre-recorded vocals.

It was leaked with mono sound but at least it's very decent and listenable!

2023 leak!
